remarks.format: ## Remarks 将多个项添加到堆栈，当使用 PushRange 是更高效的机制，而不使用一次的一个项。When adding multiple items to the stack, using PushRange is a more efficient mechanism than using one item at a time. 此外，PushRange 保证的所有元素将以原子方式，添加这意味着没有其他线程将能够插入推送的元素之间的元素。Additionally, PushRange guarantees that all of the elements will be added atomically, meaning that no other threads will be able to inject elements between the elements being pushed. 在较低的索引处的项`items`数组就会在更高版本的索引处的项之前收到推送。Items at lower indices in the `items` array will be pushed before items at higher indices. 有关代码示例，请参阅 。For a code example, see .
